<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>BudgetBuddy - Home</title>
  <link href="/css/output.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/chart.js"></script>
  <script src="https://unpkg.com/lucide@latest/dist/umd/lucide.js"></script>
</head>
<body class="bg-background text-text font-primary">
  <header class="bg-primary text-white p-4">
    <div class="container mx-auto flex justify-between items-center">
      <h1 class="text-2xl font-heading">BudgetBuddy</h1>
      <nav>
        <a href="/" class="mr-4">Home</a>
        <a href="/onboarding" class="mr-4">Onboarding</a>
        <a href="/budget" class="mr-4">Budget</a>
        <a href="/progress" class="mr-4">Progress</a>
        <a href="/about">About</a>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </header>
  <main class="min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center">
    <div class="text-center max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-heading text-primary mb-4">Your AI Companion for Smarter, Stress-Free Budgeting</h1>
      <p class="text-xl mb-8">Budgeting feels stressful and confusing. Let BudgetBuddy turn your income and goals into a clear, personalized monthly plan you can understand and control.</p>
      <div class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-heading mb-4">How it works</h2>
        <div class="flex justify-center space-x-8">
          <div class="text-center">
            <i data-lucide="user-plus" class="w-12 h-12 text-accent mb-2"></i>
            <p>1. Tell us about yourself</p>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center">
            <i data-lucide="brain" class="w-12 h-12 text-accent mb-2"></i>
            <p>2. AI generates your budget</p>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center">
            <i data-lucide="check-circle" class="w-12 h-12 text-accent mb-2"></i>
            <p>3. Track and adjust</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <a href="/onboarding" class="text-accent px-8 py-4 text-xl hover:text-secondary transition">Create My Budget</a>
    </div>
  </main>
  <footer class="bg-primary text-white p-4 mt-8">
    <div class="container mx-auto text-center">
      <p>&copy; 2026 BudgetBuddy. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </footer>
